Nc6 12. Nf5 e6 13. Nd5 $16 {[%cal Gd5b6]}) (8... Nd6 9. Bxb7 {is the same or} (
9. Bf4 Bxg2 10. Bxd6 Bh3 11. Nc3 $16 {might be even stronger})) 9. c4 $3 {
a stunning move! The position opens up even more and the check / pin on a4 is
