Nc3 {[%cal Gc3d5]} Nd7 12. Qh5 $16 {[%cal Gd4e6]}) 9. e5 Nfd7 10. Nd2 Nc6 11.
Nxc6 Bxc6 12. Nb3 $14 {[%csl Rc6][%cal Gd1g4,Gb3d4] White has a very good
