Bxf4 Nxd4 12. Bxh6 Bxh6 13. Qxd4 $16) (9... Nxf5 10. Nxf5 Rxf5 (10... gxf5 11.
Qd2 $16 {[%cal Gf2f4]}) 11. O-O d6 12. Qd2 $14) 10. Bxh6 (10. Bxd4 Nxf5 11. Bc5
d6 12. Ba3 $14 {[%cal Ge1g1,Gb2b3,Ga3b2] also is good for White}) 10... Rxf5
11. O-O d6 (11... Qb6 $2 12. Nd5 $1 Bxf2+ 13. Kh1 Qxb2 14. Bg4 $1 (14. Bf3 Rb8
15. Rb1 Qd4 16. Qe2 Bh4 17. g3 Bf6 18. g4 Re5 19. Nxf6+ exf6 20. Bd5+ {1-0 (20)
