-Tibensky,R (2442) Austria 2005}) (6... Nxd4 $2 7. Bxd4 Bxd4 8. Qxd4 Nf6 9. e5
$16 {is just bad for Black.}) 7. Nc3 O-O (7... Ng4 $5 {a typical accelerated
Dragon maneuver - Black trades a pair of knights.} 8. Qxg4 ({of course, not} 8.
