probably is not forced but if Black doesn't do it, it's not clear what else he
can do, besides sitting and watching.} (16. Rhd1 Rab8 17. Nc3 Kf8 18. Nd5 Bb2
19. Rc2 Ba3 {[%cal Ra3c5,Rf7f6,Rf8f7]}) 16... f5 $1 {the only active plan for
Black which is quite thematic for the structure.} (16... Rab8 {[%cal Rb7b5]}
17. Nc3 Nc5 18. h4 $14 {I can't name even one active plan for Black as White
