the end it might not be enough to win.} Nxe8 16. Rxe8+ Qd8 17. Rxd8+ Kc7 18.
dxc6 Rxd8 19. Bxd8+ Kxd8 20. cxd7 $16 {1/2-1/2 (26) Van Elst,A-Hogenacker,J 
