) (9... O-O 10. Bg5 $16 d6 $2 11. e5 Bxg2 12. exf6 gxf6 13. Bh6 Be4 14. Re1 Bg6
15. h4 $18 {[%cal Gh4h5]}) 10. Bxe4 Nxe4 11. Qg4 {[%cal Gg4e4,Gg4g7] the point!
} f5 $2 (11... Nf6 12. Qxg7 Rg8 13. Qh6 Rg6 14. Qe3 Nc6 15. Nxc6 dxc6 16. c4
