8... Be7 $2 {again, Black can't quickly castle because of a simple tactic.} 9.
e5 $1 Bxg2 10. exf6 Bxf1 11. fxe7 Qxe7 12. Kxf1 $16 {1-0 (25) Zivkovic,S (2298)
-Rodic,D (2113) Obrenovac 2010}) 9. Re1 {[%cal Ge4e5,Gc3d5,Gc1g5,Gd4f5]
White's threats remain the same} Qc7 (9... Qb8 {avoiding the Nc3-b5 threat but
