dxc6 Nc5 15. Bxf6+ gxf6 16. Bd5 $16 {[%cal Gd1f3,Ge1e3,Ga1e1]}) 13. f4 $16) 11.
a4 $1 {[%cal Ga4a5] a very important intermezzo} (11. Nd5 exd5 12. exd5+ Ne5
