advantage for White}) 11. h3 (11. Qd3 {is a very logical alternative which
also should be studied} d4 12. Na4 Be7 13. h3) 11... Be6 (11... Bh5 {this
automatic retreat to keep the pin doesn't give equality for Black.} 12. Bg5 d4
(12... Be7 13. Rb1 {[%csl Gb2][%cal Gg5f6,Gc3d5]} Ne4 (13... d4 14. Ne2 $14)
