{Black has just taken a free pawn on g4 - the threat g4-g5 was quite annoying.
How will you continue here to claim an advantage?} 11. O-O $1 {a beautiful
positional move - White is not in a hurry to regain the pawn.} Be7 (11... Bc5
12. Nd4 Nf6 13. Re1+ Kf8 14. Rb1 $14) 12. Nh4 $1 {[%cal Gd1g4]} Nf6 (12... Nge5
13. Nf5 O-O 14. Rb1 b6 15. c4 $1 $16 {Black's pieces are overloaded.}) 13. Rb1
